  Ways to increase supported bitrate -> increase PidBufs:
    - turn off debugging tools (+117 TPs)
    - reduce input/rateconv task halt threshold
    - make use of available SBRAM
    - reduce trace buffer size
    - reduce PicStats
    - reduce task stack size

  Verified that Patch for 2.3a does fix the video flash problem.


